videos.description: Zion Williamson shows off his handles as he jukes around for an easy layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Zion hits slick layup

videos.description: After trying to go for the steal, Zion Williamson comes back and accidentally pokes Nate Laszewski's eye.
videos.headline: Zion pokes Laszewski's eye

videos.description: Prentiss Hubb puts on a nice step-back move and drains the 3-pointer for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Hubb impresses with sweet stepback

videos.description: Zion Williamson is successful on 7-of-9 attempts in the first half as he leads all scorers with 17 points in the first half for Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion heats up for 17 points in first half) 2019/1/28 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion heats up for 17 points in first half

videos.description: The Notre Dame mascot nails a full-court putt during halftime and the crowd goes wild.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Notre Dame mascot hits full-court putt) 2019/1/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Notre Dame mascot hits full-court putt

videos.description: Zion Williamson hits the top of the square on the backboard and records a monster block in the second half.
videos.headline: Zion goes airborne for crazy block

videos.description: Zion Williamson records 26 points and nine rebounds as Duke comes into South Bend and wins by a large margin over Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion shines in South Bend) 2019/1/28 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion shines in South Bend
